WEBVTT

13:45.880 --> 13:47.430 line:80%
Last time it was a donkey!

13:47.830 --> 13:48.550 line:80%
A donkey!

13:48.710 --> 13:50.310 line:80%
Is that the same as a human?

13:51.120 --> 13:53.040 line:80%
With a whole bowl of that forced down,

13:53.040 --> 13:54.040 line:80%
forget a person—

13:54.040 --> 13:56.430 line:80%
even a full-grown donkey would drop dead!
